    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《吟游诗人的错》采用了幸存者类型的令人上瘾的循环，并添加了缺少的一件事：你的朋友。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >伙伴引擎（协作）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 别单打独斗：角色间互动可触发独特连招。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 协同效应至关重要：每个角色都拥有塑造团队阵容的独特能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195470/extras/b433f72f79dd3c99689d329ac570fcfa.poster.avif?t=1771882847\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195470/extras/b433f72f79dd3c99689d329ac570fcfa.webm?t=1771882847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195470/extras/b433f72f79dd3c99689d329ac570fcfa.mp4?t=1771882847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >谱写你的交响乐</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 建造工艺：从卡牌、物品和奖励技能中进行选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 视觉清晰度：体验生动而温馨的美术风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195470/extras/ec92aa433c2c18c5bf2729ea20063705.poster.avif?t=1771882847\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195470/extras/ec92aa433c2c18c5bf2729ea20063705.webm?t=1771882847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195470/extras/ec92aa433c2c18c5bf2729ea20063705.mp4?t=1771882847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >时间之树（元进展）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 失败即前进：死亡本就是计划的一部分。你的角色会记住每个循环，让你得以重返时间之树，升级角色并探究自身覆灭的根源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 探索谜团：为何时间线支离破碎？揭开贯穿多次通关的叙事线索。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195470/extras/0891386d3fb9daba802a5234e237289a.poster.avif?t=1771882847\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195470/extras/0891386d3fb9daba802a5234e237289a.webm?t=1771882847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195470/extras/0891386d3fb9daba802a5234e237289a.mp4?t=1771882847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>",
